author: @adabrew2310
text: To anyone having issues with the css/js references use this code: (in head): <link href="{% static "tinymce/css/prism.css" %}" rel="stylesheet"> (in body): <script src="{% static "tinymce/js/prism.js" %}"></script>  This is the proper code as per the documentation: http://romanvm.github.io/django-tinymce4-lite/advanced.html
